Category_Identifier: 208c39daa6a949d7963
Name: Data Privacy
Category_Description: Refers to the protection of personal data and the preservation of an individual's right to control their own information.
Slot:
	Id: ac6d7ff63953420ebd7
	Slot_Name: setting
	Description: The specific data privacy setting to modify.

	Id: ddbda6cc695b4af6839

	Description: The desired status for the data privacy setting.



Category_Identifier: d0a0f2891d00431ca2a
Name: Career Advancement
Category_Description: Describes the process of moving up the career ladder to a higher-level position.
Slot:
	Id: 955372b752014793898

	Description: The type of training to take for career advancement.

	Id: b4ab595d08684b9eaec

	Description: The industry for which the training is intended.

	Id: 490fa03b7e0f4a19b64

	Description: The level of training required for career advancement.

	Id: 2efb4e4d835f4201802

Category_Identifier: 2edbd61ab57545e3a2f
Name: Career Regression
Category_Description: Refers to the decline or backward movement in one's career path or level of responsibility.
Slot:
	Id: 91db80bcd46e4144a62
	Slot_Name: position
	Description: The job position or role for the regression analysis.

	Id: e6776fffd64249c2a6f
	Slot_Name: company
	Description: The company name for the regression analysis.
	Slot_Required_values: ['IBM', 'Microsoft', 'Google', 'Amazon', 'Facebook']

	Id: e3c1d9e0c07d482b97d
	Slot_Name: time_period
	Description: The time period for the regression analysis.
	Slot_Required_values: ['1 year', '2 years', '5 years', '10 years']

	Id: 97f283fa41fa452fb82
	Slot_Name: salary
	Description: The salary range for the regression analysis.
	Slot_Required_values: ['< 50k', '50k-80k', '80k-120k', '> 120k']
